It was a rare sight to behold today as members of the Lord’s Chosen Church used airplane-car to evangelize in Lagos. Some Nigerians in Lagos were left shocked after members of the Lord’s Chosen Church were spotted using a customized airplane-car to evangelize in Lagos state. The rare sight was captured in Cele bustop area of Lagos state. Nigerian journalist, Odinaka George who captured the moment revealed that some people were impressed at the innovative style employed by the church members which attracted a lot of attention from members of the public. Watch video below: When Religion meets Innovation: See how the Lords Chosen Church used their customized airplane-car to evangelize in Lagos.Had to get down from the bus to film this for the culture. pic.twitter.com/Ofu1OZhG9j